{"tid":2344943,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「世界百大帥哥」去年拿下冠軍 BTS 防彈少年團柾國被同隊的 V 給打敗了！","createTime":"2020-12-29T06:49:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T08:57:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4726800771d43b1dd8a6d99dd1fce025320400a","tid":2344943,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_0a199ab955ec9c264151ad70d8007ace/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-29/132646-890930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_0a199ab955ec9c264151ad70d8007ace%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-29%2F132646-890930.jpg&h=15a65835&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2020年「世界百大帥哥」，你的最愛上榜了嗎～？（只出道一個月的新人男團 ENHYPEN 就有三位成員上榜，非常厲害）<br />\n<br />\n由美國電影網站「TC Candler」公佈了2020年全球百大帥哥排行榜中，人氣男團 BTS 防彈少年團的成員柾國在去年拿下冠軍，今年退居第四，而同隊的哥哥V（金泰亨）則拿下了第二名，順帶一提，V也曾是2017年的冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一起來看看進入百大排行的韓國藝人有誰吧！（延伸閱讀：「世最美排行」TOP.10有四位韓國美人，BLACKPINK LISA第二、TWICE子瑜第四！）<br />\n<br />\n▼「世界百大帥哥」完整榜單公佈：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vAo2GEa1a_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvAo2GEa1a_I&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx0pSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=179917ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vAo2GEa1a_I</a><br />\n<br />\nNo.2 防彈少年團 V（2017年冠軍）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_067fc697052ec510c0516664f2785ee1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-29/132646-890931.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_067fc697052ec510c0516664f2785ee1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-29%2F132646-890931.png&h=09af092e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNo.4防彈少年團 柾國（2019年冠軍）<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_f61bf4b40e0190725912116e9a05d413/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-29/132646-890932.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.